Package: clv
Title: Cluster Validation Techniques
Version: 0.3-2.5
Authors@R: person(given = "Lukasz", family = "Nieweglowski", role =
        c("aut", "cre"), email = "wookashn@gmail.com")
Description: Contains most of the popular internal and external cluster
        validation methods ready to use for the most of the outputs
        produced by functions coming from package "cluster". Package
        contains also functions and examples of usage for cluster
        stability approach that might be applied to algorithms
        implemented in "cluster" package as well as user defined
        clustering algorithms.
Depends: cluster, class
License: GPL (>= 2)
Packaged: 2025-07-10 16:02:44 UTC; hornik
Repository: CRAN
Date/Publication: 2025-07-10 16:31:15 UTC
NeedsCompilation: yes
Author: Lukasz Nieweglowski [aut, cre]
